    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have seriously got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s been my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, it looks like it just rolled right off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve kept it in spotless condition\u2014no scratches, no spills, just pure perfection. It drives like an absolute dream and still has that fresh, new-car feel. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically flawless and ready for a new home, this is the one for you. Come say hi and take it for a spin, you're going to love it!",
