    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is an investment-grade E46 M3, showcasing a meticulously maintained S54B32 power plant. This specimen features a factory-spec 8,000 RPM redline facilitated by individual throttle bodies and a robust Double VANOS system that has been professionally bulletproofed. Power is delivered through a precise 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox to the rear wheels via an M-variable differential lock. The chassis integrity is flawless, with a reinforced rear subframe and zero evidence of fatigue. Suspension geometry remains true to factory tolerances, utilizing original equipment dampers and bushings. This is a collector-tier example with a documented service history, representing the absolute pinnacle of naturally aspirated inline-six engineering.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 18
    },
    {
