    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 2004 Honda S2000 AP2 is a masterclass in naturally aspirated performance. At its heart lies the F22C1 DOHC VTEC inline-four, delivering a linear power band and an 8,000 RPM redline. The longitudinal RWD layout is paired with a crisp, close-ratio six-speed manual transmission and a Torsen limited-slip differential for optimal traction and corner-exit stability. Its rigid X-bone frame chassis and four-wheel double-wishbone suspension provide a 50/50 weight distribution and unmatched steering feedback. This specimen remains in collector-grade condition, showcasing flawless factory paint and a pristine undercarriage. For the purist seeking a mechanically unmolested, high-revving icon, this AP2 is an unparalleled example of Japanese engineering excellence.",
